}}</ref>  Mitara yi hlamuseriwa kuri mpfhuka lowu fambiwaka hi [[rivoningo]] e ndzeni ka xihava-moya hi nkarhi wa sekende yin'we loko yi avanyisiwa hi 299 792 458.<ref name="Res1">{{cite web |url=http://www.bipm.org/en/CGPM/db/17/1/ |title=17th General Conference on Weights and Measures (1983), Resolution 1. |accessdate=19 September 2012}}</ref>

Mitara yi hlamuseriwe ro sungula hi lembe ra 1793 kuri mpfhuka wa khume hi kuleha eka timiliyoni eka [[mangwa]] wo suka e xikarhi ka [[misava]] ya e ximhandzanini xale n'walungu wa misava – hikwalaho xirhendzevutana xa misava xina magwa wa ti magidi ya ti mitara ya kwalomu ka 40,000.

